   <category name='bowling'>

      <section name='score'>

         <para number='1' comment='Bowl message - player'>
         You rub the ball in your hands and adjust your grip, then take a couple of steps and slide to the line where, with a powerful swing of your arm you release it...
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Roomex'>
         %s rubs a ball and adjusts the grip, then takes a couple of steps up to the line and with a powerful arm swing, releases it...
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Score 0 - player'>
         As you release the ball, your grip slips slightly and the ball bounces off line and goes into the gutter, rolling out of sight. You missed completely, you failed to knock any of the pins over, and you score a big fat zero. How embarrassing!
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Roomex'>
         The ball bounces off line and goes into the gutter, rolling out of sight. %s missed completely and failed to knock any of the pins over, scoring absolutely nothing. How embarrassing!
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Score is 1 - player'>
         You watch as your ball misses the pocket completely and knocks over just one pin. You score a deplorable 1 point.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Roomex'>
         The ball misses the pocket completely, knocking over just one pin. %s scores a deplorable 1 point.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Everyone'>
