      <section name='alley'>

         <para number='1' comment='Take ball away - 711'>
         As you leave the alley, an official takes the bowling ball away from you - the management doesn't allow customers to walk off with the sporting equipment!
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Turn back if wearing shoes 713'>
         You can't leave the bowling alley without returning the bowling shoes to the registration desk - and you don't want to leave your own footwear behind.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='710 - turn back if not got shoe'>
         You are not allowed to proceed any further unless you are wearing bowling shoes.
         </para>

      </section>

