      <section name='shoes'>

         <para number='1' comment='rent shoes - 648 - already got'>
         You are already wearing a pair of bowling shoes; you don't need any more.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Create shoes'>
         You hold up a foot (or whatever it is your species stands on) and the man examines it. He grunts, then passes you a pair of shoes that have clearly been worn by many others before you. Ignoring the odor of past bowlers, you remove whatever footwear you are wearing and put the bowling shoes on.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Return shoes - not got'>
         You don't have any bowling shoes to return.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Return the shoes'>
         You take off the rather smelly bowling shoes and return them to the man behind the desk. He rummages around until he finds your own footwear, which you take and put on again.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Drop bowling shoes'>
         You can't just discard the bowling shoes wherever you like - you need to get back your own footwear from the registration desk.
         </para>

      </section>

